  "title": "AB03 - Auxiliary Police Operations Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position: Auxiliary Police Officers</strong><br />Salary Package</p><ul><li>$2,820 to $5,370 gross  (armed) | Bonus of $20,000 paid in tranche</li><li>$2,610 to $4,000 gross (unarmed) | Bonus of $10,000 paid in tranche</li></ul><p>Able to work 12 hours shift<br />Location: Islandwide</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Attend to security enquiries in the premises.</li><li>Conduct armed security patrol in the premises</li><li>Consolidate incident reports.</li><li>Perform armed access control and security screenings.</li><li>Perform armed security surveillance at the command Centre.</li><li>Perform crowd control in public areas and manage traffic on the roads.</li><li>Perform law enforcement duties.</li><li>Provide armed guarding and escorting services.</li><li>Provide quick responses to incidents and emergencies.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 3 GCE ‘N’ / ‘O’ Levels / NITEC or WPLN SOA 5 and above for all 5 modules (Writing, Speaking, Reading, Listening and Numeracy)</li><li>Able to work shift duties (Including extended shift, weekends & public holidays</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
